_2014_rus.pdf \u041a\u043e\u043b\u0438\u0447\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u043e\u0431\u0441\u043b\u0443\u0436\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0445 \u043f\u0430\u0441\u0441\u0430\u0436\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432 \u0432 \u0430\u044d\u0440\u043e\u043f\u043e\u0440\u0442\u0430\u0445 \u0420\u0435\u0441\u043f\u0443\u0431\u043b\u0438\u043a\u0438 \u041a\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0445\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d \u0437\u0430 2014-2013 \u0433\u0433.\u0441\u0442\u0440 39</ref>==\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n! Rank || Airport || Region || City || IATA code || Passengers <br/> 2014\n|-\n|  1 || [[Almaty International Airport]] || [[Almaty]] || [[Almaty]] || ALA || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 4 588 885\n|-\n|  2 || [[Astana International Airport]] || [[Astana]]  || [[Astana]] || TSE || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 2 915 760\n|-\n|  3 || [[Aktau Airport]] || [[Mangystau Region]] || [[Aktau]] || SCO || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 813 964 \n|-\n|  4 || [[Atyrau Airport|ATMA Atyrau Airport]] || [[Atyrau Region]] || [[Atyrau]] || GUW || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 564 526\n|-\n|  5 || [[Shymkent International Airport]] || [[Shymkent]] || [[Shymkent]] || CIT || style=\"text-align:right;\" |442 645\n|-\n|  6 || [[Aktobe Airport]] || [[Aktobe Region]] || [[Aktobe]] || AKX || style=\"text-align:right;\" |321 800\n|-\n|  7 || [[Oskemen Airport]] || [[East Kazakhstan Region]] || [[Oskemen]] || UKK || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 277 565\n|-\n|  8 || [[Sary-Arka Airport]] || [[Karaganda Region]] || [[Karaganda]] || KGF || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 267 009\n|-\n|  9 || [[Kyzylorda Airport]] ||  [[Kyzylorda Region]] || [[Kyzylorda]] || KZO || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 152 375 \n|-\n| 10 ||  [[Pavlodar Airport]] || [[Pavlodar Region]] || [[Pavlodar]] || PWQ || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 122 488\n|-\n| 11 || [[Kostanay Airport]] || [[Kostanay Region]] || [[Kostanay]] || KSN || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 119 787\n|-\n| 12 || [[Oral Ak Zhol Airport]] || [[West K