ensr\u00ffche (EP)|Queensr\u00ffche]]'' (EP)\n* [[Quiet Riot]] \u2013 ''[[Metal Health]]''\n* Rage (UK) \u2013 ''Run for the Night''\n* [[Raven_(British_band)|Raven]] \u2013 ''[[All_for_One_(Raven_album)|All for One]]''\n* [[Ratt]] \u2013 ''[[Ratt (EP)|Ratt]]'' (EP)\n* Riff Raff \u2013 ''Give the Dead Man Some Water''\n* [[Riot (band)|Riot]] \u2013 ''[[Born in America]]''\n* Roadrunner - ''Teenage Warcry'' (EP)\n* [[Rock Goddess]] \u2013 ''[[Rock Goddess (album)|Rock Goddess]]''\n* Rock Goddess \u2013 ''[[Hell Hath No Fury (Rock Goddess album)|Hell Hath No Fury]]''\n* [[The Rods]] \u2013 ''In the Raw''\n* The Rods \u2013 ''Live'' (live)\n* [[Satan (band)|Satan]] \u2013 ''Court in the Act''\n* Satan Jokers \u2013 ''Les Fils du M\u00e9tal''\n* [[Savage (band)|Savage]] \u2013 ''Loose 'N Lethal''\n* [[Savage Grace (metal band)|Savage Grace]] \u2013 ''The Dominatress'' (EP)\n* [[Savatage]] \u2013 ''[[Sirens (Savatage album)|Sirens]]''\n* [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]] \u2013 ''[[Power & the Glory]]''\n* [[Shy (band)|Shy]] \u2013 ''Once Bitten... Twice...''\n* Silver Mountain \u2013 ''Shakin' Brains''\n* [[Sinner (band)|Sinner]] \u2013 ''Fast Decision''\n* Six Feet Under (Swe) \u2013 ''Six Feet Under''\n* [[S.A.Slayer|Slayer]] (S.A.Slayer) \u2013 ''Prepare to Die'' (EP)\n* [[Slayer]] \u2013 ''[[Show No Mercy (Slayer album)|Show No Mercy]]''\n* Sledgehammer \u2013 ''Blood on Their Hands''\n* [[Sortil\u00e8ge (band)|Sortil\u00e8ge]] \u2013 ''[[Sortil\u00e8ge (EP)|Sortil\u00e8ge]]'' (EP)\n* [[Sound Barrier]] \u2013 ''Total Control''\n* Spartan Warrior \u2013 ''Steel n' Chains''\n* [[Stampede (band)|Stampede]] \u2013 ''Hurricane Town''\n* [[Starfighters (band)|Starfighters]] \u2013 ''In-Flight Movie''\n* [[Steeler (American band)|Steeler]] \u2013 ''[[Steeler (American album)|Steeler]]''\n* [[Suicidal Tendencies]] \u2013 ''[[Suicidal Tendencies (album)|Suicidal Tendencies]]''\n* Takashi \u2013 ''Kamikaze Killers'' (EP)\n* [[Talas (band)#Talas|Talas]] \u2013 ''Live Speed on Ice'' \n* [