)|Keel]]) and former [[W.A.S.P. (band)|W.A.S.P.]] bassist Rik Fox. The band produced only one album, ''[[Steeler (American album)|Steeler]]''.\n* [[Dave Mustaine]], lead guitarist for [[Metallica]], is fired for drug/alcohol abuse, and is replaced by [[Exodus (band)|Exodus]] guitarist [[Kirk Hammett]], after which he forms the L.A. [[thrash metal]] band [[Megadeth]].\n* [[Kiss (band)|KISS]] ended the use of makeup in their act.\n* November 19: the single by [[Quiet Riot]] \"[[Cum on Feel the Noize]]\" is No. 5 on the ''Billboard'' Hot 100.\n* April 17: [[Mountain (band)|Mountain]] bassist, and [[Cream (band)|Cream]] producer, [[Felix Pappalardi]] was shot and killed by his wife [[Gail Collins Pappalardi]].\n* [[Metallica]] and [[Slayer]] both release their debut albums ''[[Kill 'Em All]]'' and ''[[Show No Mercy (Slayer album)|Show No Mercy]]''.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{Timeline box|title=[[Timeline of heavy metal music|Heavy Metal Timeline]]|before=[[1982 in heavy metal music|1982]]|after=[[1984 in heavy metal music|1984]]|year='''1983'''}}\n{{S-end}}\n{{Timeline of heavy metal and hard rock music}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1983 In Heavy Metal Music}}\n[[Category:1980s in heavy metal music]]\n[[Category:1983 in music|Metal]]\n", "text_old": "{{Year in music|1983}}\n{{Year nav topic5|1983|heavy metal music}}\n\n{{unref|date=February 2015}}This is a timeline documenting the events of [[Heavy Metal music|heavy metal]] in 1983.\n\n==Newly formed bands==\n* [[Alcatrazz]]\n* [[Autograph (American band)|Autograph]]\n*[[Bad Steve]]\n* [[Bathory (band)|Bathory]]\n* [[Bon Jovi]]\n* [[Carnivore (band)|Carnivore]]\n* [[Child's Play (band)|Child'\u01a8 Play]]\n*[[Coroner (band)|Coroner]]\n*[[Darxon]]\n* [[Death (metal band)|Death]]\n*[[Elixir (British band)|Elixir]] \n* [[Excel (band)|Excel]] (known as Chaotic Noise until 1985)\n* [[Fastway (band)|Fastway]]\n*[[Fifth Angel]]\n* [[Hagar Schon Aaronson Shrieve]]\n*[[Impaler (band)|Impaler]] \n*[[Kab\u00e1t]]\n*[[Korzus]]\n*[[Lizzy Borden (band)|Lizzy Borden]]\n* [[Master (American band)|Master]]\n* [[Megadeth]]\n*[[Melvins]]\n* [[Morbid Angel]]\n* [[Necrophagia]]\n*[[Omen (band)|Omen]] \n* [[Poison (American band)|Poison]]\n* [[Possessed (band)|Possessed]]\n*[[Razor (band)|Razor]] \n* [[Rigor Mortis (band)|Rigor Mortis]]\n*[[Rogue Male (band)|Rogue Male]]\n*[[Sacrifice (band)|Sacrifice]]\n* [[Stryper]]\n* [[Testament (band)|Testament]] (known as Legacy until 1986)\n* [[Vader (band)|Vader]]\n*[[Warrant (German band)|Warrant]] \n* [[White Lion]]\n\n==Albums & EPs==\n{{Div col|colwidth=20em}}\n* [[AC/DC]] \u2013 ''[[Flick of the Switch]]''\n* [[Accept (band)|Accept]] \u2013 ''[[Balls to the Wall]]''\n* Ace Lane \u2013 ''See You In Heaven''\n* Acid \u2013 ''Maniac''\n* [[Alcatrazz]] \u2013 ''[[No Parole from Rock N' Roll]]''\n* [[Alice Cooper]] \u2013 ''[[DaDa]]''\n* Alien (US) \u2013 ''Cosmic Fantasy'' (EP)\n* [[The Angels (Australian band)|The Angels]], aka Angel City \u2013 ''[[Watch the Red]]''\n* [[Anvil (band)|Anvil]] \u2013 ''[[Forged in Fire]]''\n* Argus - ''Argus'' (EP)\n* [[Armored Saint]] \u2013 ''[[Armored Saint (EP)|Armored Saint]]'' (EP)\n* Ashbury \u2013 ''Endless Skies''\n* [[Atomic Rooster]] \u2013 '''[[Headline News (album)|Headline News]]''\n* [[Axewitch|Axe Witch]] - ''[[The Lord of Flies]]'' \n* [[Bar\u00f3n Rojo]] \u2013 ''[[Metalmorfosis]]''\n* [[Battleaxe (band)|Battleaxe]] \u2013 ''Burn This Town''\n* [[Billy Idol]] - ''[[Rebel Yell (album)|Rebel Yell]]''\n* [[Bitch (band)|Bitch]] \u2013 ''[[Be My Slave]]''\n* Bitches Sin \u2013  ''No More Chances'' (EP)\n* Black Angels \u2013 ''Kickdown''\n* [[Blackfoot (band)|Blackfoot]] \u2013 ''[[Siogo]]''\n* [[Black Sabbath]] \u2013 ''[[Born Again (Black Sabbath album)|Born Again]]''\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]] \u2013 ''[[The Rev\u00f6lution by Night]]''\n* [[Bodine (band)|Bodine]] \u2013 ''Three Times Running''\n* [[Bow Wow (band)|Bow Wow]] \u2013 ''Holy Expedition - Live''\n* Bullet (Ger) \u2013 ''No Mercy''\n* [[Chateaux (band)|Chateaux]] \u2013 ''Chained and Desperate''\n* [[Cobra (American band)|Cobra]] \u2013 ''[[First Strike (Cobra album)|First Strike]]''\n* [[Coney Hatch]] \u2013 ''[[Outta Hand]]''\n* [[Culprit (band)|Culprit]] \u2013 ''[[Guilty as Charged (Culprit album)|Guilty as Charged!]]''\n* Cutty Sark \u2013 ''Hardrock Power'' (EP)\n* [[Alex Masi|Dark Lord]] \u2013 ''Dark Lord'' (EP) \n* [[Dedringer]] \u2013 ''Second Arising''\n* [[Def Leppard]] \u2013 ''[[Pyromania (album)|Pyromania]]''\n* [[Demon (band)|Demon]] \u2013 ''The Plague''\n* [[Diamond Head (English band)|Diamond Head]] \u2013 ''[[Canterbury (album)|Canterbury]]''\n* [[Dio (band)|Dio]] \u2013 ''[[Holy Diver]]''\n* [[Dokken]] \u2013 ''[[Breaking the Chains (Dokken album)|Breaking the Chains]]''\n* [[Earthshaker (band)|Earthshaker]] \u2013 ''Earthshaker''\n* [[Kee Marcello|Easy Action]] \u2013 ''Easy Action''\n* [[Europe (band)|Europe]] \u2013 ''[[Europe (Europe album)|Europe]]''\n* [[Exciter (band)|Exciter]] \u2013 ''[[Heavy Metal Maniac]]''\n* [[Fastway (band)|Fastway]] \u2013 ''[[Fastway (album)|Fastway]]''\n* Fist (Can) \u2013 ''In the Red''\n* [[Lita Ford]] \u2013 ''[[Out for Blood (Lita Ford album)|Out for Blood]]''\n* [[Girlschool]] \u2013 ''[[Play Dirty (album)|Play Dirty]]''\n* Gotham City - ''Black Writs'' (EP)\n* [[Grand Prix (band)|Grand Prix]] - ''Samurai''\n* [[Great White (band)|Great White]] \u2013 ''[[Out of the Night]]'' (EP)\n* [[Grim Reaper (band)|Grim Reaper]] \u2013 ''[[See You in Hell (album)|See You in Hell]]''\n* [[Hagar Schon Aaronson Shrieve|HSAS]] \u2013 ''[[Through the Fire (album)|Through the Fire]]''\n* [[Hanoi Rocks]] \u2013 ''[[Back to Mystery City]]''\n* [[Hawaii (band)|Hawaii]] \u2013 ''[[One Nation Underground (Hawaii album)|One Nation Underground]]''\n* H-Bomb \u2013 ''Coup de Metal'' (EP)\n* [[Headpins]] \u2013 ''Line of Fire''\n* [[Heavy Load (band)|Heavy Load]] \u2013 ''Stronger Than Evil''\n* Heavy Pettin \u2013 ''Lettin' Loose''\n* Hellanbach \u2013 ''Now Hear Th